${d.dims ? `- Size: ${d.dims}` : ""}
${d.surf ? `- Surface: ${d.surf}` : ""}
${d.edge ? `- Edge: ${d.edge}` : ""}
${d.style ? `- Style: ${d.style}` : ""}
${d.comp ? `- Components: ${d.comp}` : ""}

RULES:
- ONE flowing sentence-chain — no bullet points
- Include spatial positioning (where each feature is)
